{"tid":1837694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［武漢肺炎］除左醫護手足  大家都仲有野可以做","createTime":"2020-01-23T17:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T05:13:03.000Z","uid":48046,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bbb0294e6855180db315fc3e1600f190798c6c","tid":1837694,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:35:44.000Z","msg":"醫護界嘅手足都已經出左聲<br />\n隔黎POST嘅聲明其實都已經講得好清楚<br />\n假若政府唔肯回應呢幾日嘅戇鳩奶共野  唔肯封關唔肯做任何措施去保護香港人<br />\n過多幾日就會升級罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係其實除左醫護界  今次件事其實係影響晒所有香港人<br />\n其實無論講緊零售好  酒店好  就算係公共交通都唔安全<br />\n根本接觸到班蝗嘅機會係個個都咁大<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實各行各業都可以參照醫護手足嘅方式罷工！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">根據《職業安全及健康條例》（Cap509），僱主均需確保其所有在工作中的僱員的安全及健康，如僱主拒絕回應同工的防疫建議，可向工會理事反映。另外，工會現強烈呼籲各位同工做好防疫措施，如出現上呼吸道感染徵狀，應盡快求診，暫停上班，留家休息，減低傳播風險。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好比醫護界手足自己一個  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要罷就一齊罷！</span></span>"},{"pid":"677c9da679e07da581d395c39d7d7529bab71dac","tid":1837694,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:38:08.000Z","msg":"大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？<br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門！！！<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫手FB, IG, 等等地方宣傳？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"78e87a9ebff922bd92d85e0ab9269e4ad10a86f6","tid":1837694,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:41:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要罷一齊罷！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f00674b3d71b4acf56690c686c15160b443a350d","tid":1837694,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"推上去重要野！<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"77667694f86a80403188f5f27831c2980967a490","tid":1837694,"uid":48046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8FsZYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8FsZYn.png&h=f7c3eec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家睇下酒店業手足都有好大危險"},{"pid":"ad4c82c5a1116afc68c3368cf80d9383df68739a","tid":1837694,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:29:05.000Z","msg":"服務業都高危"},{"pid":"7b89dcfa5106fa377645b686bbaee533ceaf71df","tid":1837694,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T19:54:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ab92755a9b2846f32aca23eb979839f8526063c","tid":1837694,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85e3a306c6e9711687c6b7899eda95c7a2956646","tid":1837694,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T22:43:08.000Z","msg":"真係要一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46957de706c4369a4f7a6095c59aba529ac0b1d1","tid":1837694,"uid":224741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77667694f86a80403188f5f27831c2980967a490","tid":1837694,"uid":48046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8FsZYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8FsZYn.png&h=f7c3eec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家睇下酒店業手足都有好大危險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T22:45:24.000Z","msg":"唔想人幫襯啫"},{"pid":"61616a99a738ccb563b8916c19cf83f963763c0a","tid":1837694,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46957de706c4369a4f7a6095c59aba529ac0b1d1","tid":1837694,"uid":224741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu